y outside the box we have some of the industry’s top professionals and realize the value of leveraging the vast experience to advance our strategy of acquire and exploit every employee plays a role in the overall success of our organization   your opportunity starts here search career opportunities resumes submitted to this website by a third party will be considered unsolicited and will become the property of energy xxi we will not pay a referral fee for the hiring of a candidate by means of an unsolicited resume submitted directly or indirectly through this site or any other means we only pay for thirdparty referrals for resumes requested by the recruiting department from preferred vendors with whom we have a contractual agreement energy xxi provides equal employment opportunities eeo to all employees and applicants for employment without regard to race color religion gender sexual orientation gender identity or expression national origin age disability genetic information marital status amnesty or status as a covered veteran in accordance with applicable federal state and local laws energy xxi complies with applicable state and local laws governing nondiscrimination in employment in every location in which the company has facilities this policy applies to all terms and conditions of employment including but not limited to hiring placement promotion termination layoff recall transfer leaves of absence compensation and training energy xxi expressly prohibits any form of unlawful employee harassment based on race color religion gender sexual orientation gender identity or expression national origin age genetic information disability or veteran status improper interference with the ability of energy xxi employees to perform their expected job duties is absolutely not tolerated about energy xxi community outreach our operations operation overview main pass complex west delta ship shoal grand isle south timbalier onshore tariffs investor relations press releases sec fi